 
# **TITLE OF THE CHAPTER: INTRODUCTION TO TEL PEDAGOGICAL DESIGN & PEDAGOGICAL PATTERNS**

DESCRIPTION OF THE MODULE:  This Pedagogical Patterns module will mainly introduce the learner to Pedagogical 
Approaches in TEL (Technology Enhanced Learning). It contains theory with a special focus on TEL design, learning 
theories, pedagogy, pedagogical approaches and patterns, as well as self-reflection activities and useful 
practical tips that can orientate better the learner to reflect and understand the theory.  

**KEYWORDS**: *TEL design, Learning Theories, Pedagogical approaches or methods,  Pedagogical Patterns* 

